# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# .env — build args and non-secret wiring. DO NOT commit (see .gitignore).
#
# Secrets (GitLab tokens, Anthropic API key) live in .catraz/secrets/ —
# one file each, mode 0600, mounted as compose secrets into the relevant
# service. They are NEVER stored here. See docs/design/agentic-workflow/
# 05-packaging/11-compose-rework.md for the rationale.
#
# Non-secret policy (allowed_projects, branch_prefix, quotas) lives in
# .catraz/config/warden.toml — the single source of truth. Edit that file,
# not this one. The WARDEN_* env vars that used to live here have been removed.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# ── Build ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# DEV_UID: auto-derived from id -u by `catraz init` to align bind-mount ownership
# and compose-secret readability. Do NOT hand-edit — a mismatch makes /workspace,
# the warden audit logs, and the mounted secrets unreadable inside the container.
DEV_UID=1000

# Custom base instead of the bundled cpp/rust/python toolchain (pick one):
# BASE_IMAGE=ghcr.io/you/base:tag           # ready-made image (no build)
# BASE_DOCKERFILE=./docker/Dockerfile.base  # your own Dockerfile (relative to the project)
# BASE_CONTEXT=.                             # build context (default: the Dockerfile's dir)

# Claude-layer build versions — defaults shown; override to pin Node or the CLI.
NODE_VERSION=22
CLAUDE_CODE_VERSION=latest

# ── Wiring (non-secret) ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────
AUTH_MODE=subscription            # subscription | api_key
# subscription: host ~/.claude is imported read-only via `catraz sync`.
# Note: tokens refreshed in-session are NOT written back to the host;
# if auth breaks after a long pause, run `catraz sync` to re-import.
CLAUDE_CREDENTIAL_SOURCE=~/.claude

# GitLab endpoint (non-secret — warden uses it to route REST calls).
# Leave as-is for gitlab.com; set to your self-hosted instance otherwise.
GITLAB_URL=https://gitlab.com

# Advanced: remote-control invocation tuning (rarely changed).
# CLAUDE_RC_SPAWN=same-dir
# CLAUDE_RC_DEBUG_FILE=
# CLAUDE_RC_EXTRA_ARGS=

# Change if 3128 is taken; also update http_port in .catraz/config/squid.conf.
# SQUID_PORT=3128

# ── Warden policy (env fallbacks — SSOT is .catraz/config/warden.toml) ───────
# WARDEN_ALLOWED_PROJECTS=
# WARDEN_BRANCH_PREFIX=
# WARDEN_MAX_OPEN_MRS=
# WARDEN_MAX_OPEN_BRANCHES=
# WARDEN_MAX_WRITES_PER_HOUR=
